[i]Rivalry[/i] – Whenever an opponent attacks with two or more creatures, draws their second card each turn, or casts their second spell each turn, distribute three +1/+1 counters among any number of creatures you control.
[i]Defiant Strength[/i] – Whenever Leonie, The Blade Breaker II attacks a player alone, double her power until end of turn.
Promoted Class – {R}{W}
